name: Deactivate and Activate unit from unit list screen

testSteps.description: Given User is on work order sign in page
When User sign in with valid credential of Account Owner
And User tap on the "Facilities" link from side navigation
Then User is on detail screen
When User clicks on "Deactivate" icon on list page
Then Success message "Facility has been deactivated successfully." should be displayed
